At least ADCs now have some sort of defensive option that won't be situational {{item:3026}} 
I'm not sure if the shield is better than the old 12% damage reduction, which it probably is since it negates all damage and not only the last person you attacked. It will probably be looked at again.
And even if that's true, what melee would buy PD? Yasuo? He has his unlimited miniondashes anyways)
